DataMigrate.Model

Class MigratorModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataMigrate.Model.MigratorModel

  • public class MigratorModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This class perform all of the operations associated with transferring data from one database file to another database file via using .csv files. Created by Anthony Orio on 4/24/2017.

                               throws java.sql.SQLException
        Creates a collection of EstimationObject that will contain all of the information pertaining to one row in the Baseline table. These objects will be used to write to the database after creating them.
        Parameters:
        baseline - The baseline name.
        cprs - The CPRS.
        month - The staff month.
        day - The staff day.
        doc - The CPDD Document.
        upgrade - The budget upgrade.
        maint - The budget maintenance.
        ddr - DDR.
        unit - Unit test weight.
        integ - Integration weight.
        design - Design weight.
        code - Code weight.
        estDefault - Default.
        date - CPPD date.
        Throws:
        java.sql.SQLException - If the SQL query could not be completed.
